{"consensus_set_id":"94327","translation_language":"fa","translation_source":{"hid":"375909"},"segments":[{"source_hadith_segment":"<quranic_text> « لَئِنْ اَنْجَيْتَنٰا مِنْ هٰذِهِ لَنَكُونَنَّ مِنَ الشّٰاكِرِينَ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ يونس ۲۲ ] </footnote>   <quranic_text> « اِنَّ اللّٰهَ بِالنّٰاسِ لَرَؤُفٌ رَحِيمٌ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ البقرة ۱۴۳ ] </footnote>   <quranic_text> « وَ نُنَزِّلُ مِنَ الْقُرْانِ مٰا هُوَ شِفٰاءٌ وَ رَحْمَةٌ لِلْمُؤْمِنِينَ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ الاسراء ۸۲ ] </footnote>   .","translation_segment":"اگر از این نجات یابیم شاکر خواهیم بود) (که خدا بمردم روف و مهربان است) (و قرآن را فرستادیم که قسمتی از آن شفاء و رحمت مومنان است).","segment_columns":[{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"لئن","display":"لَئِنْ"},{"kind":"word","token":"انجيتنا","display":"اَنْجَيْتَنٰا"},{"kind":"word","token":"من","display":"مِنْ"},{"kind":"word","token":"هذه","display":"هٰذِهِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"لنكونن","display":"لَنَكُونَنَّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"من","display":"مِنَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"الشاكرين","display":"الشّٰاكِرِينَ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"يونس","display":"يونس"},{"kind":"word","token":"۲۲","display":"۲۲"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"ان","display":"اِنَّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"الله","display":"اللّٰهَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"بالناس","display":"بِالنّٰاسِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"لرؤف","display":"لَرَؤُفٌ"},{"kind":"word","token":"رحيم","display":"رَحِيمٌ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"البقره","display":"البقرة"},{"kind":"word","token":"۱۴۳","display":"۱۴۳"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token